  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium heat",
    "Rinse the rice and soak it in water for 30 minutes",
    "Drain the rice and grind it into a coarse powder using a food processor",
    "Heat the olive oil in a pan over medium heat and saute the ground rice until lightly toasted",
    "Add the salt, black pepper, parsley, and mint to the pan and stir well",
    "Grill the castelvetrano olives for 2-3 minutes on each side until slightly charred",
    "Add the grilled olives to the pan and stir well",
    "Squeeze the lemon juice over the pilaf and stir well",
    "Spoon the pilaf onto the banana leaves and serve immediately"
